These are Puzzles for 6x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, water, 7up
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, spinach, mango, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, camping, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, security-guard, videographer, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, rock, metal, indie
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, surfing, volleyball, basketball
 1. the freelancer is on the far right##1
 2. the person drinking water is the fan of disco##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is the person eating nectarine##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the videographer is between the person who's sport is rowing and the fan of indie##2
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the fan of disco is on the right of the designer##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is between the videographer and the person eating nectarine##2
11. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
12. the freelancer is the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the fan of metal is between the fan of rock and the person who's hobby is camping##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | 7up        | mirinda       | water  | fanta |
| Food          | nectarine     | mango         | spinach     | eggplant    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking  | rock-climbing      | camping   | chess     |
| Job           | security-guard | designer | videographer   | freelancer     |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | metal         | disco | indie         |
| Sport         | basketball     | rowing     | surfing  | volleyball       |

