.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, tea, lemonade, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, traveling, video-games, puzzles
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, crime, satire, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, reggae, funk, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, russian, polish, chinese
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, subway, snowmobile
 1. the russian is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person driving the motorbike##2
 2. the chinese is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the indonesian##1
 4. the russian is between the person drinking cola and the person driving the subway##2
 5. the fan of soul is the person drinking tea##1
 6. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 8. the person driving the subway is between the person watching sports movies and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
 9. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
11. the fan of soul is the person watching satire movies##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the polish is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee    | tea       | lemonade   | cola |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing     | video-games   | puzzles    | traveling  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | satire | crime   | comedy     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | soul       | reggae | funk        |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish   | russian     | indonesian    |
| Transport     | quad-bike       | subway        | snowmobile      | motorbike        |

