.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, mirinda, almond-milk
There 4 different types of food: cucumber, apple, blueberry, artichoke
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, french, pakistani, german
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, snake, goat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, skiing, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, car, ship, trike
 1. the french is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person eating apple is on the left of the german##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person drinking mirinda##1
 6. the owner of the goat is on the far right##1
 7. the person driving the trike is between the pakistani and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the person drinking cola is between the person driving the trike and the owner of the rabbit##2
10. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
11. the person drinking almond-milk is the person driving the ship##1
12. the person eating blueberry is the person driving the car##1
13. the owner of the snake is between the person eating cucumber and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | cola        | soy-milk | almond-milk      |
| Food          | cucumber   | blueberry       | apple          | artichoke   |
| Nationality   | turkish     | pakistani    | french      | german  |
| Pet           | rabbit    | snake     | chinchilla       | goat      |
| Sport         | volleyball | cricket    | skiing        | surfing |
| Transport     | boat       | car | trike           | ship   |

