The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, mystery, spy, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, german, egyptian, nigerian
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, van, train
 1. the person drinking tea is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the egyptian##2
 2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the project-manager##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 4. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 5. the nigerian is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 7. the doctor is on the left of the brazilian##1
 8. the person driving the van is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person driving the bike is between the doctor and the person who's hobby is biked-games##2
10. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is biked-games is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
12. the videographer is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
13. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
14. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
