 1. the egyptian is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is between the person driving the ship and the person watching horror movies##2
 5. the japanese is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
11. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
12. the russian is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
13. the person drinking tea is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |      3       |      4      |
