.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, water, tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, collecting, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, country, jazz, gospel
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, canadian, argentine, american
4 different pets are kept: turtle, frog, goldfish, hedgehog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, climbing, skiing, biathlon
 1. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the dutch is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the fan of jazz##2
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is the fan of r&b##1
 6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the canadian is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the argentine is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is card-games is the dutch##1
10. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking tea##1
11. the fan of country is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the argentine is on the left of the person drinking water##1
13. the canadian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | tea | water      | coffee | 7up |
| Hobby         | singing | card-games      | collecting  | video-games        |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | country      | gospel    | r&b          |
