The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, cricket, skateboarding
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person drinking tea##2
 2. the spanish is on the left of the thai##1
 3. the owner of the goat is between the japanese and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
 4. the pilot is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the journalist is on the far left##1
 6. the german is the journalist##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the pilot##1
 8. the journalist is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 9. the journalist is the person drinking water##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the librarian##1
11. the person drinking tea is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
12. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
13. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
14. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
