.:: Puzzle 6x4-Level-2-15::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, lemonade, tea
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lettuce, nectarine, cucumber
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, mechanic, librarian, dressmaker
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, gospel, punk, hip-hop
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, brazilian, indonesian, egyptian
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the indian##1
 2. the indonesian is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 3. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the librarian##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is between the scientist and the person eating cucumber##2
 7. the egyptian is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the far left##1
 9. the egyptian is the person eating garlic##1
10. the mechanic is the owner of the rabbit##1
11. the fan of punk is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
12. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the goldfish##1
13. the fan of punk is on the right of the dressmaker##1

