10. the russian is on the right of the pakistani##1
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's hobby is video-games##2
12. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
13. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

